               <msContents>
                  <summary>One of the 70 Mughal documents including farmāns, ḥukmnāmah, iqrārnāmah, chaknāmah etc. relating to the family of <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied" key="person_f1694" role="oth" change="#role-assignment">Jalāl al-Dīn, <foreign xml:lang="fa">جلال الدین</foreign>
                     </persName>, Qāz̤ī of the pargana Batala, Punjab, and his escendents dated <date calendar="#Gregorian" from="1527" to="1757">from 1527 to 1757</date>
                  </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="IO_Islamic_4720.4-item1" defective="unknown" class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008115922">
                     <author key="person_f5537">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied">Ṣadr al-Ṣudūr Sayyid Aḥmad</persName>
